---
// Hero component for NetCoin website
---

<section class="hero">
    <h1>The Future of Decentralized Networking</h1>
    <p>
        Building on Bitcoin's revolutionary Proof of Work and Jason Lowery's Softwar vision,
        NetCoin extends these groundbreaking concepts into the realm of global network infrastructure.
        Earn NTC tokens by contributing to planetary-scale internet routing through useful computational work.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="#about" class="btn btn-primary">Discover NetCoin</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/netcoin-ntc/netcoin" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Code</a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  background: var(--gray-900);
  color: var(--light);
  padding: 120px 20px 100px;
  text-align: center;
  min-height: 90vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--light);
}

.hero p {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  opacity: 0.95;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.7;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

.cta-buttons {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

.btn {
  padding: 16px 32px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  display: inline-block;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.btn::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: -100%;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
  transition: left 0.5s;
}

.btn:hover::before {
  left: 100%;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #d97706);
  color: white;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.05);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
}

.btn-secondary {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  color: white;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.btn-tertiary {
  background: var(--gray-800);
  color: white;
  border: 2px solid var(--gray-800);
}

.btn-tertiary:hover {
  background: var(--gray-700);
  border-color: var(--gray-700);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* Advanced button effects */
.btn::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
  border-radius: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: width 0.6s, height 0.6s;
}

.btn:active::after {
  width: 300px;
  height: 300px;
}

/* Mobile responsiveness */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero {
    padding: 80px 20px 60px;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn {
    width: 220px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
}
</style>
